name: We're all gonna make it
description: Wow. 1st off, congratulations to everyone who made this possible, whether you're a veteran artist or a newcomer, it just shows the power of creative communities. I was going to make this a 1/1 but what better way to to do the opposite than for a momentous occasion. As for me, it's almost been a whole year since I began my digital/crypto/nft journey, and here we fking are...
